
TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Central Banker as a Risk Manager: Estimating the Federal Reserve's Preferences under Greenspan
AU  - KILIAN, LUTZ
AU  - MANGANELLI, SIMONE
Y1  - 2008/09/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1538-4616.2008.00150.x
